{"tid":696304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論，其實呢條賤種算唔算係怨婦嘅表表者？","createTime":"2018-06-10T03:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T07:03:14.000Z","uid":41158,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef19f4115d5e5935789024be77d06c887c3f357","tid":696304,"uid":41158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>Jose Mourinho's Liverpool complex masks a grudging respect for the club that spurned him</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe bad blood was renewed a few months later in the Champions League semi-final, when Mourinho&rsquo;s Chelsea were eliminated by Luis Garcia&rsquo;s &ldquo;ghost goal&rdquo;, which still vexes him to this day.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/liverpool-manchester-united-jose-mourinho-complex-snub-grudging-respect-jurgen-klopp-a7997696.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fpremier-league%2Fliverpool-manchester-united-jose-mourinho-complex-snub-grudging-respect-jurgen-klopp-a7997696.html&d=bQY5POVczabMtXcoPhFxK10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f3cc3f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/liverpool-manchester-united-jose-mourinho-complex-snub-grudging-respect-jurgen-klopp-a7997696.html</a><br />\n<br />\n十四日就叫怨婦<br />\n咁十四年都嚟緊叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b6175bb2fdd3c92eec1f84317894619b9b2568","tid":696304,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"因愛成恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb01333fad7d041091e76f5b2bdf5847f2abd67","tid":696304,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"總之就親親Da